{"tid":1090993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子葵涌飛墮平台　頭爆肢折身亡","createTime":"2019-04-04T00:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T06:00:23.000Z","uid":160807,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df00d3f2cfbd5be34465d2e2d5ba68f41c60b798","tid":1090993,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/photo/bkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190404011354\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190404011354&h=3aff20ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌青山公路葵涌段430-436號偉賢樓，今晚(4月3日)8時許，上址平台突然傳來巨響，住客循聲查看，赫見一名男子倒臥平台昏迷，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，證實男事主已頭爆肢折，當場死亡，消防其後將遺體移至地面。 <br />\n<br />\n警方在場未有檢獲遺書，經初步調查後，相信36歲姓陳男事主由大廈天台跨過欄河，一躍而下飛墮至3樓平台，事件無可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190403%2Fbkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001.html&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5DcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=7c8c2525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190403/bkn-20190403224639072-0403_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"24edd1afdbb7a093476be39cbb5d31ac5880482a","tid":1090993,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"5fa466543310bc11de589ed66696b3300a85333d","tid":1090993,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"24edd1afdbb7a093476be39cbb5d31ac5880482a","tid":1090993,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:50:56.000Z","msg":"."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"7191147cdb40c7ec72108dc37d09113e9708964f","tid":1090993,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"